data.description: Discover unparalleled comfort and style in this stunning 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home, boasting an array of upgrades and amenities that promise a luxurious living experience. As you step through the front door, the grandeur of the 2-story foyer immediately captivates you, setting the tone for the elegant design that flows throughout the property. To the right, a bright and airy separate living and dining room awaits, perfect for hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet moments. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the spacious, upgraded eat-in kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a coveted double oven, and ample cabinet space for all your culinary needs. Overlooking the sunken family room, this kitchen becomes the perfect backdrop for creating memories with loved ones. The main level is further enhanced by new flooring and a convenient half bathroom, offering both style and functionality. The full finished basement is a treasure trove of additional living space, featuring tile flooring, a game or exercise room, a large bedroom, and a full bathroom with a dual walk-in shower, ideal for guests or as an in-law suite. The outdoor living space is equally impressive, with stone paved flooring, under-decking with recessed lighting and fan, and an expansive deck above, creating an oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Upstairs, the owner's suite with a luxurious bathroom and walk-in custom closets, along with 3 additional large bedrooms and a full bathroom, complete this exquisite home. Located just minutes from shopping, restaurants, and a golf course, and with easy interstate access, this home combines convenience with sophistication, making it a truly exceptional place to live.
